<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc4392fba-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87" identifier="/us/usc/t38/s8528"><num value="8528">§ 8528.</num><heading> Investment of the Fund</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Money in the Fund not required for current disbursements may be invested and reinvested by the Secretary of the Treasury in interest-bearing obligations of the United States or in obligations guaranteed as to both principal and interest by the United States.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idc4392fbb-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87">(<ref href="/us/pl/85/857">Pub. L. 85–857</ref>, <date date="1958-09-02">Sept. 2, 1958</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/72/1262">72 Stat. 1262</ref>, § 5228; renumbered § 8528, <ref href="/us/pl/102/40/tIV/s402/b/1">Pub. L. 102–40, title IV, § 402(b)(1)</ref>, <date date="1991-05-07">May 7, 1991</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/105/238">105 Stat. 238</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
